        API documentation, and cloud technologies. Specializing in transforming complex technical 
        concepts into engaging user experiences.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a
          href="#projects"
          class="rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-blue-600 transition-colors"
        >
          View Projects
        </a>
        <a href="#contact" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
          Contact Me <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span>
        </a>
